<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="Aink375">
<l>ituveṉ pāvai pāvai yituveṉ</l>
<l>ṉalamaru nōkki ṉalamvaru cuṭarnutaṟ</l>
<l>paiṅkiḷi yeṭutta paiṅkiḷi yeṉṟivai</l>
<l>kāṇṭoṟuṅ kāṇṭoṟuṅ kalaṅka</l>
<l>nīṅkiṉa ḷōveṉ pūṅka ṇōḷē</l>
      </lg>
      <lg type="translation" xml:lang="en">
<l>“This is the doll of my doll[-like daughter], </l>
<l>[and] this is the green parakeet raised by my green parakeet [girl] </l>
<l>of confused glances and beautiful, shining forehead”, - </l>
<l>whenever [I] look at them, [I’m] saddened –  </l>
<l>has my flower-eyed girl [indeed] left? </l>
      </lg>
    </div>
